        "product_description": {
            "value": "The GEAR AID Revivex Down Care Kit is a complete solution for cleaning, restoring, and repairing your favorite down-filled gear, including jackets, vests, blankets, and sleeping bags. This kit includes a fragrance-free Revivex Down Cleaner that gently washes away dirt, body oils, and odors that can compromise the loft and warmth of down insulation. The concentrated formula is safe for use in a standard washing machine and helps restore the natural loft and performance of your gear so it feels fresh and stays warm. To keep your equipment in top condition, the kit also comes with Tenacious Tape Mini repair patches that quickly and permanently fix holes, tears, and burns without sewing or heat. Simply peel and stick to seal punctures and prevent down from escaping. Ideal for outdoor enthusiasts, campers, and backpackers, this all-in-one care kit extends the life of your insulated gear and keeps it performing season after season.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
